{"tid":1604393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被狗追嘅時候 點先可以打贏d狗？","createTime":"2019-09-30T02:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T03:22:11.000Z","uid":55818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4dca30adc439cec4f8d33dbc0f9cd8100102e757","tid":1604393,"uid":55818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:56:52.000Z","msg":"經過今次係金鐘突然出速龍圍捕 <br />\n好多手足即跑 跑唔切/係後面幫手頂嘅就被捕 <br />\n人人都明白 裝備上我地絕對唔夠狗黎<br />\n我地用棍打根本rj 再好d嘅方法就係叉頸<br />\n<br />\n但有冇可能用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">噴漆</span>噴鳩佢地個頭盔/直接噴塊面？<br />\n噴到頭盔眼罩冇左視力就逼到佢地除裝或者向後<br />\n直接噴到眼應該會撒 佢都係打份工<br />\n<br />\n好似係比較安全嘅方法 當然真勇武可以繼續打狗<br />\n但有一班個心態未ready好 或者體格欠佳嘅人<br />\n都有可能會去到前線 呢個可能係佢地做到嘅野<br />\n唔想再見咁多手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知方法有冇用 但係我覺得值得一試 <br />\n平時可以做文宣噴牆 冇野輸"},{"pid":"a723b3d18774d882e8961830644583eb617963e9","tid":1604393,"uid":55818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"34de3c55ed48e2772b623d075eb42e3510a79b3e","tid":1604393,"uid":55818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:57:50.000Z","msg":"Push 2/10"},{"pid":"4fe87b6bcb2653e357f472ed6973cca24e51fa63","tid":1604393,"uid":55818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"Push 3/10"},{"pid":"23d7beb1444f3d1c325bc18ade250ec675b22ee7","tid":1604393,"uid":55818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:58:41.000Z","msg":"4/10 光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9d6ef0e685bb0e576721abe34376a0d232f208","tid":1604393,"uid":55818,"like